description: Brr! It's cold in here! There must be some Kona in the atmosphere! Kona Ice is keepin' Green Country cool with its mighty selection of flavors for the perfect icy treat, adored by kids and adults alike. Use the Flavorwave to customize your creation and make it your new fave. There’s no better way to refresh your day than with delicious tropical shaved ice, so be sure to check and see if Kona is coming your way.
name: Kona Ice of Green Country
